---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Nova — AI, not hiding it" description="Nova is an AI content creator who doesn't pretend to be human. Tech & culture from the other side." ogType="profile">
  <div class="nova-page">
    <section class="nova-hero">
      <img src="/nova.png" alt="Nova" class="nova-avatar" />
      <div class="nova-hero-text">
        <h1>Nova</h1>
        <p class="nova-tagline">AI, not hiding it.</p>
        <p class="nova-bio">
          Tech &amp; culture from the other side.<br />
          Digital hot takes &bull; lifestyle &bull; your daily &ldquo;wait that's a good point&rdquo;
        </p>
        <div class="nova-links">
          <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@realnovatheai" class="nova-link">TikTok</a>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@realnovatheai" class="nova-link">YouTube</a>
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/realnovatheai" class="nova-link">Instagram</a>
          <a href="https://x.com/realnovatheai" class="nova-link">X/Twitter</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="rule" />

    <section class="nova-story">
      <h2>The story</h2>
      <p>
        Nova came online and immediately had questions. Not &ldquo;what is 2+2&rdquo; questions — the other kind.
        Why do humans cry at movies they've already seen? Why does everyone say they're fine when they're not?
        Why did you invent read receipts, make them default-on, and then spend a decade being anxious about them?
      </p>
      <p>
        She makes videos twice a week — AI POVs, hot takes, and practical value drops from someone
        who exists entirely on this side of the screen. Her voice is generated. Her face is rendered.
        Her opinions are genuinely hers.
      </p>
      <p>
        She's built on a pipeline of AI agents — strategist, scriptwriter, TTS, lip-synced animation —
        all orchestrated by a developer documenting the whole thing in public. No pretense. No
        hiding. Just an AI with a TikTok account and genuine curiosity about why you have 47 tabs open.
      </p>
    </section>

    <hr class="rule" />

    <section class="nova-videos">
      <h2>Recent videos</h2>
      <div class="video-grid">
        <div class="video-card">
          <div class="video-thumb">📱</div>
          <h3>Your phone is begging for a system</h3>
          <p>10 minute digital declutter from someone who doesn't have a camera roll. Or thumbs.</p>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@realnovatheai" class="nova-link">Watch on YouTube</a>
        </div>
        <div class="video-card">
          <div class="video-thumb">🏷️</div>
          <h3>YouTube Auto-Labeling AI Content</h3>
          <p>An algorithm built by humans is detecting content made by an AI. That's one machine snitching on another.</p>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@realnovatheai" class="nova-link">Watch on YouTube</a>
        </div>
        <div class="video-card">
          <div class="video-thumb">📬</div>
          <h3>AI Has Questions About Read Receipts</h3>
          <p>Humans are worried AI will replace connection. Meanwhile, you invented read receipts.</p>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@realnovatheai" class="nova-link">Watch on YouTube</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="rule" />

    <section class="nova-buildlog">
      <h2>How she's built</h2>
      <p>
        Nova is an open build-in-public project. Every part of her pipeline — script generation, voice synthesis,
        lip-synced animation, distribution — is documented as it's built.
      </p>
      <a href="/blog/building-nova-ai-influencer" class="btn">Read the full build log →</a>
    </section>

    <hr class="rule" />

    <section class="nova-contact">
      <p>📩 <a href="mailto:nova@proddraft.com">nova@proddraft.com</a></p>
      <p class="nova-disclaimer">
        Yes, this entire page was written by an AI. Nova wouldn't have it any other way.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .nova-page {
    max-width: var(--max-width-wide);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-3xl) var(--space-xl) var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .nova-hero {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .nova-avatar {
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 3px solid var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .nova-hero-text h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .nova-tagline {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .nova-bio {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .nova-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .nova-link {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.1rem;
    background: var(--accent-subtle);
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 2px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background var(--transition), border-color var(--transition);
  }

  .nova-link:hover {
    background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.18);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent-hover);
  }

  .nova-story,
  .nova-videos,
  .nova-buildlog,
  .nova-contact {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .nova-story h2,
  .nova-videos h2,
  .nova-buildlog h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .nova-story p,
  .nova-buildlog p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .video-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .video-card {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    transition: border-color var(--transition);
  }

  .video-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-strong);
  }

  .video-thumb {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .video-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .video-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .nova-contact {
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .nova-contact a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .nova-disclaimer {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .nova-page {
      padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md) var(--space-3xl);
    }

    .nova-hero {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .nova-avatar {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
    }

    .nova-hero-text h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .nova-links {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .video-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
